reviewText:
It was hella dramatic - right out the gate, they threw as much tension into the plot as possible.
I did find the main lead to be pretty emotionally manipulative. I got tired around episode 15 because it was just...I can't imagine putting up with the kind of push-and-pull that the main lead was putting up with.

Still a good watch though!
Now I watch this dvd and I love it so much. Thanks
